title: Skrillex Live at the Alfa Future People Festival, Nizhny Novgoro
description:
Huge shout outs to Sergei Shevtsov for bringing us this whole performance done by Skrillex in Nizhny Novgorod at the Alfa Future People Festival. This crazy set shows Sonny in a completely different stage set up to a completely different crowd from normal - the ending is simply breathtaking.

Yes, the set in Verona was also on the 12 - time zone difference :)
